        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "I am writing to offer some valuable feedback on the cookery course that I did last month from your renowned school.",
        "I would like to start by thankig you and your team for tutoring students with so much patience. Because the course was so thorough, I never faced any difficulty in comprehending the details. After learning to cook a wide variety of cuisines from such a well-known institute , I believe I will have an array of opportunities in the future.",
